{
  "name": "Reverse Seal Summoning",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Non%20Elemental.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You mark up to 6 willing Creatures with a chakra seal, marking them with your personal seal formation. With this seal, you can, as a bonus action, teleport creatures marked with your seal, to you, from up to 1 mile away. You may also Inversely teleport to them, as a bonus action, from up to 300 Feet away, occupying a space within 5 feet of them that can hold you. Creatures marked can resist being summoned causing this jutsu to fail, if they resist you do not spend chakra.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above A-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and multiply the range by 10.</p>",
